OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FDylan Thomas, 24, the grandson of a
OL,7,Fpie company tycoon, has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor life with a minimum term of 19
OL,9,Fyears for the murder of his friend
OL,10,FWilliam Bush, 23, at their home in
OL,11,FLlandaff, Cardiff.
OL,13,FWilliam Bush, 23, was killed by Dylan
OL,14,FThomas, his childhood friend and the
OL,15,Fgrandson of businessman Sir Stanley
OL,16,FThomas, on December 24, 2023.
