OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FThomas had been staying at his
OL,7,Fgrandmother's house in Rhoose, in the
OL,8,FVale of Glamorgan, the night before he
OL,9,Fattacked Mr Bush. He begged her to
OL,10,Ftake him back to his house, insisting
OL,11,Fhe wanted to walk his dog, Bruce.
OL,13,FHis grandmother sat in the car while
OL,14,Fhe went inside. But he returned
OL,15,Fminutes later, banging on the window
OL,16,Fcovered in blood.
