OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FAt the sentencing hearing, 24-year-old
OL,7,FThomas watched via video link from
OL,8,FAshworth High Secure hospital, as
OL,9,Fmoving victim impact statements were
OL,10,Fread to Cardiff Crown Court.
OL,12,FMr Bush's sister Catrin spoke on
OL,13,Fbehalf of herself and her brother Alex
OL,14,F` describing her brother's death as a
OL,15,F"barbaric crime".
OL,17,F"I cannot put into words how traumatic
OL,18,Fand awful this experience was, and I
OL,19,Fstill have intense moments of panic
OL,20,Fwhen I think about this," she said.
