OL,6,F"Myself and Alex cannot begin to
OL,7,Fcomprehend the fear and suffering that
OL,8,FWill endured on that day. We are truly
OL,9,Fhaunted from the horror of it and this
OL,10,Fwill live with us forever."
OL,12,FThomas's grandfather, Sir Stanley, the
OL,13,Ffounder of Peter's Pies ` whose net
OL,14,Fworth was estimated to be #230 million
OL,15,Fin 2013, sat in court throughout the
OL,16,Fsentencing.
