OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FMr Bush, a keen golfer who played for
OL,7,Fhis country, had been friends with
OL,8,FThomas since they were about 13,
OL,9,Fhaving met at Christ College Brecon, a
OL,10,Fprivate boarding and day school in mid-
OL,11,FWales.
OL,13,FDuring the trial, the jury heard from
OL,14,FDr Panchu Xavier, a consultant
OL,15,Fforensic psychiatrist at Ashworth, who
OL,16,Fsaid the defendant could have been
OL,17,Fhaving a psychotic episode during the
OL,18,Fattack and for "up to six months
OL,19,Fbefore the event".
