OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FThe jury also heard Thomas had been
OL,7,Farrested for breaking into Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace a few months before the attack
OL,9,Fon Mr Bush.
OL,11,FThomas told officers he was looking
OL,12,Ffor "energy fields" between the Palace
OL,13,Fand Cleopatra's Needle, an obelisk in
OL,14,Fcentral London.
OL,16,FHe was rugby-tackled by an officer
OL,17,Fafter he told them he was "over now so
OL,18,Fyou may as well show me round".
