OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FWilliam Bush's father, John, told
OL,7,FCardiff Crown Court the lives of his
OL,8,Ffamily changed overnight when his son
OL,9,Fdied and the effects would stay with
OL,10,Fthem forever.
OL,12,FHe said in a victim impact statement:
OL,13,F"This is not normal grief, where death
OL,14,Fis part of human existence and loss
OL,15,Fcan be accepted and memories of loved
OL,16,Fones celebrated. We are not there yet,
OL,17,Fand there is not yet any closure for
OL,18,Fus.
