OL,6,F"We carry on with our own lives, but
OL,7,Fwe know we are always pretending. We
OL,8,Fhave also had to watch the pain of the
OL,9,Floss for Will's brother Alex and
OL,10,Fsister Catrin, and their partners, Ed
OL,11,Fand Olivia, and Will's girlfriend Ella.
OL,13,F"We will share their future happiness,
OL,14,Fbut we will always be tinged with
OL,15,Fsadness and loss. We continue with our
OL,16,Flives because we must, but time cannot
OL,17,Ffully heal the loss of Will's.
