OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,F"Imagine all the things that you would
OL,7,Fhave missed if you had died at 23 `
OL,8,Fmarriage, children, family, the daily
OL,9,Fjoys of the life. His life mattered.
OL,10,FGod bless you, Will."
OL,12,FWilliam Bush's partner Ella Jefferies
OL,13,Ftold Cardiff Crown Court in a victim
OL,14,Fimpact statement how they were
OL,15,Fplanning their future lives together
OL,16,Fwhen he died.
OL,18,F"To lose Will has meant we have lost
OL,19,Fthe future that we have both planned
OL,20,Fand prepared for," she said.
