OL,6,F"Will and I had achieved a lot in the
OL,7,Fyear that we were together.
OL,8,FUltimately, I have lost a person that
OL,9,FI love.
OL,11,F"To lose a person that you love so
OL,12,Funexpectedly and in such a horrific
OL,13,Fway has left an indescribable pain and
OL,14,Fa darkness in my life.
OL,16,F"Will was petrified of dying and to
OL,17,Fknow he was alone and died from such
OL,18,Fhorrendous injuries leaves me with
OL,19,Fsuch pain."
