OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend to death on
OL,4,CChristmas Eve handed life sentence
OL,6,FSentencing, Mrs Justice Steyn paid
OL,7,Ftribute to the bravery of William
OL,8,FBush's family, describing the victim
OL,9,Fas a "compassionate, loving, witty and
OL,10,Fvibrant young man" who was
OL,11,F"senselessly murdered."
OL,13,FThe judge added that no sentence could
OL,14,Fmake up for the loss of Mr Bush, and
OL,15,Fthat it was clear that his family was
OL,16,F"haunted daily" by what had happened.
